+"""
+GTSAM Copyright 2010-2018, Georgia Tech Research Corporation,
+Atlanta, Georgia 30332-0415
+All Rights Reserved
+Authors: Frank Dellaert, et al. (see THANKS for the full author list)
+
+See LICENSE for the license information
